groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:name: Tie a Yellow Ribbon 'Round.........
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:placed_by: Monitored by Binky Del Mar,placed by Jr High Scifi
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:short_description: A few steps at the trail head, hard packed gravel path from there. A few small ups and downs nothing bad. About 5-10 feet of off trail, grass could hide a snake or ticks, just a warning.
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:long_description:
A beautiful walk around a vineyard. Along the way there is a gazebo, picnic tables and several places to take great pictures. ENJOY!
BYOP, Room for small TBs and geocoins as well as other small trading items.
**Big Thanks to Binky Del Mar, she is monitoring/sponsoring this cache.**
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:encoded_hints: Old Oaky doensn't like you looking at his old war wound, cache is on the otherside

groundspeak:log.groundspeak:text: Came here for company meetings, had to get a cache while I was here. My first in CA. TFTC!
I dropped off Coast Guard. He barely fit, so hopefully someone will give him some breathing room soon.
